TEXT.S: = Sima-un = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Jnaysyang ka alang Sima-un. 209 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 817 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 94% niqan 770 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 6% niqan 47 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun 88%, Tayal 3%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 2%.
